then glad I could help.

00:20:20.095 --> 00:20:22.013 position:50% align:center
[MIREI]
What a memorable centennial.

00:20:22.097 --> 00:20:24.557 position:50% align:center
I'd go so far as to bet
this year's festival

00:20:24.641 --> 00:20:26.643 position:50% align:center
was the most fun it's ever been.

00:20:26.726 --> 00:20:30.689 position:50% align:center
Yeah, and if we're lucky,
it'll continue.

00:20:30.772 --> 00:20:32.607 position:50% align:center
Decade after decade.

00:20:32.691 --> 00:20:34.776 position:50% align:center
With a new group of
promising young students

00:20:34.859 --> 00:20:37.487 position:50% align:center
passing the baton every time.

00:20:37.570 --> 00:20:40.657 position:50% align:center
By the way, why'd you
pick that girl to sub?

00:20:40.740 --> 00:20:42.659 position:50% align:center
Oh, not for any major reason.

00:20:42.742 --> 00:20:44.202 position:50% align:center
It was a reward.

00:20:44.285 --> 00:20:47.080 position:50% align:center
I figured she deserved it for
standing up for her friend.

00:20:47.163 --> 00:20:48.832 position:50% align:center
--Well...
--Huh?

00:20:48.915 --> 00:20:51.418 position:50% align:center
Also, she may have gushed
about my performance

00:20:51.501 --> 00:20:54.838 position:50% align:center
as Oscar ten years ago,
without knowing it was me.

00:20:54.921 --> 00:20:56.756 position:50% align:center
I guess I couldn't really
help myself.

00:20:56.840 --> 00:20:57.841 position:50% align:center
A-ha!

00:20:59.175 --> 00:21:01.720 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER] And now, we can
present the final results!

00:21:01.803 --> 00:21:03.263 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER B]
That's right!

00:21:03.346 --> 00:21:05.598 position:50% align:center
Without further ado, the winners
of the Grand Sports Festival

00:21:05.682 --> 00:21:08.977 position:50% align:center
for this very special
Centennial year are...

00:21:09.060 --> 00:21:10.687 position:50% align:center
...The Spring Troupe!

00:21:10.770 --> 00:21:12.105 position:50% align:center
[RYUU]
Yes!

00:21:13.523 --> 00:21:15.650 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER B] With all the grace
and elegance of a cherry blossom

00:21:15.734 --> 00:21:18.778 position:50% align:center
tree in bloom, The Spring
Troupe and their illustrious

00:21:18.862 --> 00:21:21.990 position:50% align:center
Ryuu Asahina
have grasped victory!

00:21:22.073 --> 00:21:23.366 position:50% align:center
Thank you all.

00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:25.493 position:50% align:center
The festival is over,
but we hold the Kouka spirit

00:21:25.577 --> 00:21:28.705 position:50% align:center
in our hearts, now and forever.

00:21:28.788 --> 00:21:30.957 position:50% align:center
We hope you thoroughly
enjoyed the show.

00:21:31.041 --> 00:21:32.208 position:50% align:center
[AUDIENCE cheers]

00:21:32.292 --> 00:21:34.127 position:50% align:center
We're grateful that
you're all here.

00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:37.964 position:50% align:center
and for the chance to put our
awesome teamwork on display,

00:21:38.048 --> 00:21:40.592 position:50% align:center
making this Sports Festival
one truly worthy

00:21:40.675 --> 00:21:42.677 position:50% align:center
of this momentous year.

00:21:42.761 --> 00:21:45.722 position:50% align:center
And from all of us who are
members of the Kouka troupe,

00:21:45.805 --> 00:21:48.767 position:50% align:center
thank you for your
continued support!

00:21:48.850 --> 00:21:50.435 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCERS]
One last round of applause!

00:21:50.518 --> 00:21:52.520 position:50% align:center
[AUDIENCE cheers]

00:21:58.360 --> 00:22:00.487 position:50% align:center
[CHIAKI] Everything went
off without a hitch.

00:22:00.570 --> 00:22:02.197 position:50% align:center
[YAMADA]
I was so nervous!

00:22:02.280 --> 00:22:03.990 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah, I was too,

00:22:04.074 --> 00:22:05.950 position:50% align:center
but we all got to
have so much fun,

00:22:06.034 --> 00:22:07.869 position:50% align:center
and I learned so many
important new things

00:22:07.952 --> 00:22:09.871 position:50% align:center
that'll keep helping
me on my way.

00:22:09.954 --> 00:22:12.624 position:50% align:center
If the next Sports Festival
is in ten years,

00:22:12.707 --> 00:22:14.459 position:50% align:center
then, you know what?

00:22:14.542 --> 00:22:17.837 position:50% align:center
We'll be the ones up there,
gracefully leading our teams!

00:22:17.921 --> 00:22:18.963 position:50% align:center
Think about that!